# Summit Agenda Consistency

For every `content/*/agenda.md`:

- Keep the heading format:
  - `## The agenda: [start day] to [end day] [Month] [Year]`
- Required columns: `Date`, `Speaker`, `Topic`
- Optional columns:
  - Time as 2nd column with empty header
  - `Resources` as final column (post-summit, when links exist)
- Column order must be:
  - `Date` -> `(Time)` -> `Speaker` -> `Topic` -> `(Resources)`

Resources conventions:

- Use explicit link labels by type:
  - `Video (SlidesLive)`, `Video (YouTube)`, `Slides`, `Demo`, `Resources`
- Do not use vague labels like `Click here`.
- Keep one resource entry per session row when resources are available.
